    public class LongHashMap<V>
extends BasicWrapper<LongObjectHashMapHandle>
    A wrapper around the internal LongHashMap implementation. This type of HashMap allows storing values at long keys. Ideally, two int values are merged into one long to map against 2D-coordinates. This type of class is used by, for example, the internal chunk storage.
